name: EngineeringDaily.net
description: News, Notes and Jobs for engineering pro
overview:
EngineeringDaily.net is a news/articles/discussions magazine by and for in-the-trenches engineers. This website provides relevant and important information for those working in the engineering discipline.

The creation of EngineeringDaily.net was necessitated by the lack of a conducive web medium through which like-minded engineering professionals can interact productively. EngineeringDaily.net aims to provide this much-needed forum.

This website also provides interactive brain games and a platform on which engineers can showcase their services and increase relevant traffic to their own websites.
